_sText:
A Zombie Mod map in CBBLE style.
It's a remake of the zm_cbble_b3_fixed map.
Has many places to hide, some places to barricade, and a little jail(you can get there by the teleport(find it yourself). To break the jail you should break the thing under it which is holding the jail!)
Boards which are thrown through the crates, as well as to the fortress, and from her, can be broken!
Map made specially for a server "clan by[Zombie Attack]..."
If you put it on your server, please inform me about it!
